    -   Verify that a right-side drawer opens instead of a modal.
    -   Test the stepper functionality (Project Name -> Git Provider selection).
    -   Verify that clicking "Next", "Back", and "Cancel" works as expected.
    -   Connect to a Git provider (mock or real) if possible to ensure the flow continues correctly.
2.  **Upload SBOM Drawer:**
    -   Click the "Upload SBOM File" button.
    -   Verify that a right-side drawer opens instead of a modal.
